@model dynamic

@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Hadouken — A headless BitTorrent client for Windows";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Hadouken</h1>
    
    <p class="lead">
        Hadouken is a headless, cross-platform BitTorrent client with a low memory footprint.
        It is perfect for seedboxes, media servers and other server setups.
    </p>
    
    <p>
        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-success" href="https://github.com/hadouken/hadouken/releases/latest">Download</a>
    </p>
</div>

<div class="row marketing">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h3><i class="fa fa-github"></i> Open source
        </h3>
        <p>
            We believe in open source and so should you. <a href="https://github.com/hadouken/hadouken">The source code for Hadouken</a>
            is hosted on GitHub and includes everything needed to build it yourself.
        </p>

        <h3><i class="fa fa-puzzle-piece"></i> Plugins
        </h3>
        <p>
            Hadouken features a powerful JavaScript API and is bundled with a few different plugins
            covering the basic needs. The API is well-documented and easy to use.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6">
        <h3><i class="fa fa-group"></i> Community driven
        </h3>
        <p>
            It is the community that makes Hadouken so frickin' awesome. Ideas, plugins and general epicness
            all comes from the community. We &lt;3 you.
        </p>

        <h3><i class="fa fa-smile-o"></i> No ads, no bullshit
        </h3>
        <p>
            We aim to make you happy, and that is why you will never see ads on this site, in the installer
            or in the web interface. We also do not try to shove crapware and toolbars down your throat.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
